{"tid":598012,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"好心神秘台唔好放在學術台上","createTime":"2018-03-19T07:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T10:49:35.000Z","uid":149978,"like":22,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2daacc48d82ae069f9ee004fe596f141b8a2e53b","tid":598012,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:03:16.000Z","msg":"每次一係神秘台post野，<br />\n講下超自然野，<br />\n實有班科學撚、歷史撚和哲學撚出黎踩場。<br />\n<br />\n當正神秘台真係學術台post咁討論。<br />\n<br />\n狙擊完，攻擊一返，再自high。<br />\n<br />\n好心啦，講明係神秘台，又話人地膠，又話乜冇「可證偽性」。<br />\n<br />\n離左題去狙擊，又當自己好醒<br />\n<br />\n其實最大問題都係連登admin<br />\n將神秘台放入學術台中<br />\n<br />\n明知連登仔好多都唔戴眼鏡睇野<br />\n將神秘台當學術台post咁睇<br />\n<br />\n支持神秘台獨立成台<br />\n支持神秘台脫離學術台<br />\n<br />\n支持新增宗教台"},{"pid":"8f46d0b1ad4bfdca68c8c0d3751f6e0a6797a71e","tid":598012,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:08:24.000Z","msg":"人柒就咩台出post都柒架啦"},{"pid":"b1b6553a8038752db2a6d7a81edb0f7faa40c82a","tid":598012,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"最尾一句想點？突然變咗宗教台？<br />\nUFO 光明會 古文明 Kennedy遇蝕 算乜嘢宗教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3232a6483e6573f77a58953f3dcfb7cab30deee9","tid":598012,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b1b6553a8038752db2a6d7a81edb0f7faa40c82a","tid":598012,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"最尾一句想點？突然變咗宗教台？<br />\nUFO 光明會 古文明 Kennedy遇蝕 算乜嘢宗教？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:20:18.000Z","msg":"Sor 睇漏新增 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n升神秘台做主台先"},{"pid":"9a55e7f4d5f8ae77d84eb102dc575530926cba16","tid":598012,"uid":43721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"不如神秘post既人去content farm討論啦<br />\n反正都廢話連篇"},{"pid":"2203d1653cd4da03b200f6bfdafc40